             were indicted for <rs id="t18270712-1-off1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18270712-1-off1" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18270712-1-off1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="burglary"></interp>
               burglariously breaking and entering the dwelling-house of 
                     <persName id="t18270712-1-victim91" type="victimName">
                        Andrew Berkeley 
                        Drummond
                     <interp inst="t18270712-1-victim91" type="surname" value="Drummond"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18270712-1-victim91" type="given" value="Andrew Berkeley"></interp>
